title: Legacy Palettes Plugin
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

The Legacy Palettes Plugin contains the nineteen [[colour palettes|ColourPalettes]] that shipped in the core of ~TiddlyWiki prior to v5.5.0, including ~SolarizedDark, ~SolarizedLight, Nord and ~GruvBoxDark.

<<.from-version "5.5.0">> Install this plugin from the official plugin library to continue using these palettes in an upgraded wiki.
